The committee shall consist of ten (10) members as follows:
The president or a designee of:
Kentucky Association of the Deaf; and
Kentucky Registry of Interpreters for the Deaf;
A representative from:
Kentucky Commission on the Deaf and Hard of Hearing (KCDHH);
Eastern Kentucky University Interpreter Training Program;
Kentucky Department of Education;
Kentucky Office of Vocational Rehabilitation;
Kentucky School for the Deaf; and
Cabinet for Health and Family Services; and
Two (2) members at large, who are consumers, appointed by the board.
